# Project 01 â€“ Identity Foundation & Access Model

## Objective
Establish a secure identity foundation using Microsoft Entra ID by implementing user accounts, security groups, and MFA.

## Tasks Completed
- Created test users in Entra ID
- Created security groups
- Assigned users to groups
- Enabled Security Defaults (MFA)
- Documented procedures in a runbook

## Access Model
Access is assigned using security groups rather than direct user permissions to follow least-privilege principles.

## Artifacts
- Identity-Foundation-Runbook.pdf
- Screenshots located in the screenshots folder

## Skills Demonstrated
- Identity and Access Management (IAM)
- User provisioning
- Group-based access control
- MFA implementation
- IT documentation

